What?

876
00:35:39,510 --> 00:35:40,300
When the show is over,

877
00:35:40,300 --> 00:35:41,530
arrange for the others to get on the bus

878
00:35:41,530 --> 00:35:42,360
and leave immediately.

879
00:35:42,360 --> 00:35:44,020
We'll settle the wages later.

880
00:35:44,050 --> 00:35:46,050
No problem. They're all our people.

881
00:35:46,070 --> 00:35:46,900
Tell the rest of us

882
00:35:46,900 --> 00:35:47,840
to pack up our things

883
00:35:47,840 --> 00:35:48,800
and wait for me in the car.

884
00:35:48,800 --> 00:35:49,570
I'll go get the final payment.

885
00:35:49,570 --> 00:35:50,150
After I come back,

886
00:35:50,150 --> 00:35:51,420
we'll leave immediately too.

887
00:35:51,420 --> 00:35:52,820
What's going on?

888
00:35:55,960 --> 00:35:56,440
What?

889
00:35:57,690 --> 00:35:59,770
Okay. I'll go inform them right away.

890
00:36:05,390 --> 00:36:07,350
[Singing Along the Way]

891
00:36:07,860 --> 00:36:09,000
[Singing Along the Way]

892
00:36:16,840 --> 00:36:18,280
Ram your way out!

893
00:36:23,300 --> 00:36:24,760
If I said you couldn't leave,

894
00:36:24,760 --> 00:36:25,960
then you can't leave.

895
00:36:26,760 --> 00:36:27,460
What are you doing?

896
00:36:27,460 --> 00:36:28,720
It's fine. Don't move.

897
00:36:29,870 --> 00:36:31,520
Hey, brothers.

898
00:36:31,540 --> 00:36:33,530
Don't smash the car.

899
00:36:33,650 --> 00:36:34,380
Be careful.

900
00:36:34,440 --> 00:36:36,170
You can smash me instead, okay?

901
00:36:36,190 --> 00:36:37,890
We borrowed this car.

902
00:36:37,920 --> 00:36:38,530
What's the meaning of this?

903
00:36:38,530 --> 00:36:39,500
Open the gate.

904
00:36:39,530 --> 00:36:41,100
Sir, what's going on?

905
00:36:41,440 --> 00:36:42,240
Open the gate?

906
00:36:43,670 --> 00:36:44,980
Is this your territory?

907
00:36:44,980 --> 00:36:46,130
Is this your territory?

908
00:36:46,130 --> 00:36:47,210
No, no, don't.

909
00:36:47,280 --> 00:36:48,690
Bro! Bro!

910
00:36:49,400 --> 00:36:51,100
Listen to me.

911
00:36:51,820 --> 00:36:53,690
We've finished the performance,

912
00:36:53,710 --> 00:36:54,150
right?

913
00:36:54,260 --> 00:36:56,050
We all have each other's numbers, right?

914
00:36:56,050 --> 00:36:58,180
When you come to Beijing in the future,

915
00:36:58,730 --> 00:37:00,030
I'll buy you a drink.

916
00:37:00,130 --> 00:37:02,320
Have a smoke.

917
00:37:03,050 --> 00:37:04,880
I paid a lot of money to invite you here.

918
00:37:04,880 --> 00:37:07,000
You want to leave
before the business is done?

919
00:37:07,000 --> 00:37:08,800
Why is this guy so unreasonable?

920
00:37:09,110 --> 00:37:11,090
You can go wherever you want.

921
00:37:11,090 --> 00:37:11,380
No.

922
00:37:11,380 --> 00:37:12,460
Leave the 2 girls behind.

923
00:37:12,460 --> 00:37:13,130
Don't.

924
00:37:14,730 --> 00:37:15,660
What do you mean?

925
00:37:15,800 --> 00:37:16,530
Don't move.

926
00:37:16,550 --> 00:37:17,880
Or I'll call the police.

927
00:37:18,000 --> 00:37:18,930
Call the police?

928
00:37:20,280 --> 00:37:21,380
Let go!

929
00:37:21,400 --> 00:37:22,250
We're doomed.

930
00:37:25,480 --> 00:37:26,530
What are you doing?

931
00:37:26,530 --> 00:37:27,530
-Go away!
-Scram!

932
00:37:27,610 --> 00:37:28,380
Get away!

933
00:37:28,460 --> 00:37:30,020
Don't touch me!

934
00:37:30,090 --> 00:37:31,610
Let me go! What are you doing?

935
00:37:31,610 --> 00:37:32,280
Let go!

936
00:37:32,340 --> 00:37:33,180
Let go!

937
00:37:33,230 --> 00:37:34,020
Let go!

938
00:37:34,460 --> 00:37:35,190
Are you okay?

939
00:37:50,550 --> 00:37:51,480
Let's see who dares to make a move.

940
00:37:51,480 --> 00:37:52,630
Just try it.

941
00:37:52,710 --> 00:37:53,320
Go ahead.

942
00:38:02,390 --> 00:38:03,940
You were frightened, weren't you?

943
00:38:03,940 --> 00:38:05,870
What matters is that we're unhurt.

944
00:38:06,090 --> 00:38:06,860
I didn't expect to encounter

945
00:38:06,860 --> 00:38:09,000
such a thing on a performance tour.

946
00:38:09,050 --> 00:38:10,920
If the police hadn't arrived in time,

947
00:38:10,920 --> 00:38:11,960
we'd have been helpless.

948
00:38:11,960 --> 00:38:12,760
You're right.

949
00:38:13,690 --> 00:38:15,150
None of us expected it.

950
00:38:15,590 --> 00:38:16,510
But no matter what,

951
00:38:16,510 --> 00:38:17,440
as the director,

952
00:38:18,230 --> 00:38:20,360
I want to apologize to everyone first.

953
00:38:21,920 --> 00:38:23,120
When you're out and about,

954
00:38:23,120 --> 00:38:24,920
you can meet all kinds of people.

955
00:38:24,980 --> 00:38:25,980
It's very normal.

956
00:38:26,060 --> 00:38:26,450
Tell me,

957
00:38:26,450 --> 00:38:28,650
what would you do if this happens again?

958
00:38:29,000 --> 00:38:31,000
If the police hadn't arrived in time

959
00:38:31,020 --> 00:38:32,250
and controlled the situation this time,

960
00:38:32,250 --> 00:38:33,510
wouldn't we have been done for?

961
00:38:33,510 --> 00:38:34,820
We have ladies in our group, too.

962
00:38:34,820 --> 00:38:36,670
Should we prepare some tools?

963
00:38:37,100 --> 00:38:38,500
Well,

964
00:38:38,740 --> 00:38:40,650
let me say a few words.

965
00:38:40,970 --> 00:38:43,350
Recently,

966
00:38:43,380 --> 00:38:45,840
everyone has indeed worked hard.

967
00:38:46,160 --> 00:38:48,030
But we've made good money, too.

968
00:38:48,060 --> 00:38:48,740
Right?

969
00:38:49,190 --> 00:38:49,800
If it really doesn't work out,

970
00:38:49,800 --> 00:38:51,590
let's take a break for a while.

971
00:38:51,780 --> 00:38:53,510
Our Singing Along the Way trope

972
00:38:53,580 --> 00:38:55,840
needs to rest and recharge.

973
00:38:55,860 --> 00:38:56,700
Right?

974
00:38:57,760 --> 00:38:58,660
Right.

975
00:38:58,680 --> 00:39:00,240
It wasn't our fault this time.

976
00:39:00,240 --> 00:39:02,100
We should carry on as usual.

977
00:39:02,390 --> 00:39:04,310
Let's have a good meal.

978
00:39:05,840 --> 00:39:07,860
Yes, carry on as usual.

979
00:39:07,990 --> 00:39:09,920
Don't take everything to heart.

980
00:39:10,100 --> 00:39:11,840
We'll eat, drink, and chat

981
00:39:11,860 --> 00:39:14,080
to our heart's content.

982
00:39:14,880 --> 00:39:16,200
That's right.

983
00:39:16,230 --> 00:39:16,790
Right?

984
00:39:17,130 --> 00:39:18,250
Right, Zhuang Zhuang?

985
00:39:18,250 --> 00:39:18,970
Yes.

986
00:39:19,230 --> 00:39:20,240
It's no big deal.

987
00:39:20,270 --> 00:39:21,520
It's no big deal.

988
00:39:24,140 --> 00:39:25,480
Finally back in Beijing.

989
00:39:25,480 --> 00:39:26,340
Give me a smile.

990
00:39:27,110 --> 00:39:28,230
I can't smile.

991
00:39:28,590 --> 00:39:30,510
You were terrified just now, weren't you?

992
00:39:30,510 --> 00:39:31,690
I was scared to death.

993
00:39:31,690 --> 00:39:33,220
I'm still reeling even now.

994
00:39:34,160 --> 00:39:35,810
My arm was pulled so hard it hurts.

995
00:39:35,810 --> 00:39:37,470
How about I massage it for you?

996
00:39:38,070 --> 00:39:39,210
I learned how.

997
00:39:39,240 --> 00:39:40,580
-No need.
-It’s like playing the saxophone.

998
00:39:40,580 --> 00:39:41,090
Let me massage it for you.

999
00:39:41,090 --> 00:39:42,690
It'll swell even more later.

1000
00:39:45,140 --> 00:39:45,660
Ranran,

1001
00:39:50,340 --> 00:39:51,940
I have something to give you.

1002
00:39:52,270 --> 00:39:53,290
What is it?

1003
00:39:55,550 --> 00:39:56,090
Ranran.

1004
00:39:58,080 --> 00:39:59,170
Wait a moment.

1005
00:40:06,240 --> 00:40:11,380
[Luogu Hutong]

1006
00:40:07,230 --> 00:40:08,560
Why are you here?

1007
00:40:08,580 --> 00:40:09,740
I've been calling you these past few days.

1008
00:40:09,740 --> 00:40:10,620
Why didn't you answer?

1009
00:40:10,620 --> 00:40:11,550
Where did you go?

1010
00:40:11,870 --> 00:40:14,130
I was on a performance tour with friends.

1011
00:40:16,620 --> 00:40:17,260
Ranran,

1012
00:40:17,360 --> 00:40:18,000
if you haven't had

1013
00:40:18,000 --> 00:40:18,770
any acting roles recently,

1014
00:40:18,770 --> 00:40:19,670
You could have told me.

1015
00:40:19,670 --> 00:40:21,120
I'd have figured something out.

1016
00:40:21,120 --> 00:40:22,650
Why are you running performances?

1017
00:40:22,650 --> 00:40:24,320
Isn't it just a waste of time?

1018
00:40:25,410 --> 00:40:26,940
Are you here for something?

1019
00:40:27,260 --> 00:40:28,440
There is a project.

1020
00:40:28,460 --> 00:40:29,820
The director has his eyes on you

1021
00:40:29,820 --> 00:40:30,750
after he watched

1022
00:40:30,750 --> 00:40:31,640
your performance in

1023
00:40:31,640 --> 00:40:32,800
"Golden Garden at Sunset."

1024
00:40:32,800 --> 00:40:35,590
This is a big project.
Opportunities like this are rare.

1025
00:40:35,590 --> 00:40:36,250
Tonight,

1026
00:40:36,280 --> 00:40:37,560
the producer and the director
have a dinner party.

1027
00:40:37,560 --> 00:40:38,430
Hurry up and come with me.

1028
00:40:37,770 --> 00:40:39,820
[Luogu Hutong]

1029
00:40:45,060 --> 00:40:46,370
Do I have to go today?

1030
00:40:48,570 --> 00:40:50,650
It's now or never.

1031
00:40:50,960 --> 00:40:51,920
Your call.

1032
00:41:03,780 --> 00:41:04,520
Liangliang,

1033
00:41:04,770 --> 00:41:06,210
Mr. Chu told me

1034
00:41:06,400 --> 00:41:07,470
there's a big project,

1035
00:41:07,470 --> 00:41:08,860
and he wants me to give it a try.

1036
00:41:08,860 --> 00:41:11,360
The director and people from the studio
will be there.

1037
00:41:11,360 --> 00:41:12,750
Have dinner without me.

1038
00:41:12,880 --> 00:41:14,460
Can you tell Zhuang Zhuang for me?

1039
00:41:14,460 --> 00:41:16,680
Okay, I'll let them know.

1040
00:41:16,840 --> 00:41:18,300
I'll get going then.

1041
00:41:18,760 --> 00:41:19,280
Bye.

1042
00:41:21,440 --> 00:41:23,260
[Luogu Hutong]

1043
00:41:50,230 --> 00:41:53,180
Wild geese are flying south.

1044
00:41:53,260 --> 00:41:56,580
Wild geese are flying south.

1045
00:41:57,190 --> 00:42:03,360
The cries of wild geese break my heart.

1046
00:42:03,440 --> 00:42:05,280
Stop singing.

1047
00:42:05,360 --> 00:42:06,280
What's with you now?

1048
00:42:06,280 --> 00:42:07,430
What are you up to?

1049
00:42:07,500 --> 00:42:08,900
The finalist list is out.

1050
00:42:08,980 --> 00:42:09,590
It's out?

1051
00:42:10,210 --> 00:42:12,690
Look! You made it to the finals!

1052
00:42:11,610 --> 00:42:12,070
[National Singer Competition
Organizing Committee]

1053
00:42:12,090 --> 00:42:12,790
[Notice of participation
in the National Singer Competition]

1054
00:42:14,380 --> 00:42:15,830
That's splendid.

1055
00:42:16,080 --> 00:42:18,010
[Notice of participation
in the National Singer Competition]

1056
00:42:18,070 --> 00:42:20,070
Zhuang Zhuang, congratulations.

1057
00:42:20,170 --> 00:42:20,840
You are now

1058
00:42:20,840 --> 00:42:22,650
getting closer and closer to your dream.

1059
00:42:22,650 --> 00:42:23,880
Stay composed.

1060
00:42:23,880 --> 00:42:24,590
You must keep your composure.

1061
00:42:24,590 --> 00:42:25,090
At this point,

1062
00:42:25,090 --> 00:42:26,260
your mindset is the most important.

1063
00:42:26,260 --> 00:42:27,460
Eat well, sleep well,

1064
00:42:27,480 --> 00:42:28,650
and prepare for the competition.

1065
00:42:28,650 --> 00:42:30,570
Practice more and take more classes.

1066
00:42:30,570 --> 00:42:31,630
Isn't it only a few months away?

1067
00:42:31,630 --> 00:42:31,890
Yes.

1068
00:42:31,900 --> 00:42:33,360
Arrange more classes for Zhuang Zhuang.

1069
00:42:33,360 --> 00:42:34,110
For free, okay?

1070
00:42:34,110 --> 00:42:36,280
-It’s free. It’s definitely free.
-I’ll ask her mom

1071
00:42:36,280 --> 00:42:37,280
to make a few more outfits for me

1072
00:42:37,280 --> 00:42:37,940
instead.

1073
00:42:37,980 --> 00:42:39,780
So that's what you're thinking.

1074
00:42:40,000 --> 00:42:41,260
Thank you, Mrs. Zheng.

1075
00:42:41,320 --> 00:42:42,300
Thank you, Mr. Zheng.

1076
00:42:42,300 --> 00:42:43,160
Zhuang Zhuang.

1077
00:42:45,070 --> 00:42:46,310
I wish you success,

1078
00:42:46,710 --> 00:42:48,440
and that your dream comes true.

1079
00:42:50,050 --> 00:42:50,500
Okay.

1080
00:42:52,010 --> 00:42:52,460
All the best!
